title: How to Handle Being Unsatisfied with Life Ft. Alyssa Bethke
description: Have you ever felt unsatisfied in life? Maybe you want a relationship, a different body, to live in a different place, or a different career. In today's episode, Alyssa, author of "Satisfied", joins us to talk about how to identify being unsatisfied and how to handle it.  Leave us a review! Want to send Jeanine a message?
